            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Imperator Caesar, son of the divine Antoninus, grandson of the divine Hadrian, great-grandson of the divine Trajan (conqueror) of Parthia, great-great grandson of the divine Nerva, Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Augustus, pontifex maximus, holder of tribunician power for the 16th time, consul for the 3rd time. The 7th cohort of watchmen (erected this).</p>
